    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Luxury Sport SUV that strikes the perfect balance between performance and utility. The exterior is finished in a deep Metallic Charcoal; the paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway commuting. The alloy wheels are wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport tires with plenty of tread depth remaining, and the brake rotors show no signs of warping or heavy grooving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of black leather and brushed aluminum. The upholstery is supple and free of punctures or heavy stains, though there is some light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster from regular entry and exit. Every feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium surround-sound system\u2014is fully operational. Mechanically, this vehicle is solid. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil service and cabin filter replacement performed just 500 miles ago. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. While it shows the honest signs of a car that has been enjoyed, it remains a reliable, clean, and impressive example of the model. Non-smoker owned and garage-kept.",
